                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">This is a cross post from the WoW off-topic forums, but I felt it was important enough to pass along.  This didn't happen to me but someone else, but I think you'll agree they deserve our support.
<br />

<br />
 I know this is a bizzare place to post something of this nature. and I'm not here to 'sob' I'm here to look for some support. In a nutshell . on April 23rd, 2004, my sister died in a fatal car accident. We're originally from Canada and moved here; she was driving to my grandmothers wedding (remarried <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" /> She was stopped on the Illinois state-highway #126, there was a school bus stopped on the road with those blinking 'stop' signs out. Behind that was a stopped Cement truck; behind that was my 22 year old sister in a black dodge neon. 
<br />

<br />
There was a 15 ton eighteen wheeler with over 1/2 a mile stopping distance who 'failed to notice' the car, school bus and the cement truck. He didn't stop .. ran right over my sister in the dodge neon. According to the coroner (when I had to ID the body irl  <img src="images/smiles/icon_sad.gif" alt="icon_sad.gif" border="0" /> )
<br />

<br />

<br />
There was carbon and 'soot' in her lungs, she was alive trapped under the dashboard of her car, the fuel tanks on the eighteen wheeler ruptured on the top of the dodge neon when it went over and the full desiel fuel tank leaked onto my trapped sister. It was estimated she was alive in the fire for 10 minutes and burnt alive. Criminally he was issued a 'failure to stop', which currently in illinois state law is a 75$ traffic minor traffic offence. He still drives today, and paid nothing more than a parking ticket. We're trying to get this changed, so that there won't be another dead sibling elsewhere, or atleast something with out atleast some repercussions, we have an active petition going and it can be signed online by the hyperlink posted below, it was written by my mother, (apparently she found the caps lock <img src="images/smiles/icon_wink.gif" alt="icon_wink.gif" border="0" /> and my sisters name was Shannon Orr (I'm Dylan Orr <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" />
<br />

<br />
Thank you for the time in reading this 'blog' and thank you for your support with this.
<br />

<br />
Petition Link ==> <a href="http://www.ipetitions.com/campaigns/Fatal" target="_blank">http://www.ipetitions.com/campaigns/Fatal</a>
<br />

<br />
Anyone in the USA can sign <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />When a government has ceased to protect the lives, liberty and property of the people, from whom its legitimate powers are derived, and for the advancement of whose happiness it was instituted, and so far from being a guarantee for the enjoyment of those inestimable and inalienable rights, becomes an instrument in the hands of evil rulers for their oppression. - Declaration of Independence of the State of Texas.</span><span class="gensmall"><br /><br />Last edited by Twizlewink on Tue Mar 01, 2005 11:54 am; edited 1 time in total</span></td>
